column5: Hey all, I was wondering if anyone could tell me how far up the West branch of the 16 mile do the resident brookies and browns start holding? Also do the salmon make it that far up?(I can imagine they would greatly disturb the resident trout fishing..?).  Any info would be greatly appreciated.  Thank, Jakub
Welcome aboard Bowman. Just a quick word of advice, take a look at the introductions of some of the recent new members here.
